STATE of Iowa, Plaintiff-Appellee,
v.
Angelia Maurice SCHULTZ, Defendant-Appellant. No. 18-0818 Court of Appeals of Iowa. Filed January 9, 2019

DECISION WITHOUT PUBLISHED OPINION See Iowa R. App. P. 6.904

Angelia Schultz appeals following her guilty plea to operating a motor vehicle while intoxicated, third or subsequent offense. AFFIRMED.

AFFIRMED.
